(39, 1, '2008-01-22 22:22:31', '2008-01-23 03:22:31', '\r\n<p class="dropcap"> Upgrade Wordpress from 2.3.1 to 2.3.2, WordPress 2.3.2 is an urgent security release that fixes a bug that can be used to expose your draft posts. 2.3.2 also suppresses some error messages that can give away information about your database table structure and limits and stops some information leaks in the XML-RPC and APP implementations.</p>\r\nI found that the "zip" and the "tar" package r some what different. The version number in "zip" file is 2.2.3, but the number in "tar" file is 2.2.1. Is this a mistake? :(', 'Upgrade Wordpress to 2.3.2', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'update-wordpress-to-232', '', '', '2008-01-24 23:30:56', '2008-01-25 04:30:56', '', 0, 'http://sealence.x10hosting.com/wordpress/?p=39', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(40, 1, '2008-01-25 02:09:45', '2008-01-25 07:09:45', '\r\n<p class="dropcap"> Previously I said the version of wordpress was 2.2.3, it turned out to be the problem of my download programm "Thunder". It will found all the useable mirrors, but not the newest one. This is the reason why I got the wrong vesion. Opps! :evil:</p>', 'Thunder downloaded the wrong version of wordpress', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'thunder-downloaded-the-wrong-version-of-wordpress', '', '', '2008-02-04 03:13:45', '2008-02-04 08:13:45', '', 0, 'http://sealence.x10hosting.com/wordpress/?p=40', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(41, 1, '2008-02-13 20:44:37', '2008-02-14 01:44:37', '\r\n<p class="dropcap"> For the Spring Festival, I went home and spend my holidays with my families in WuZhou. I had happy times and hard times. My dear dog - WangWang had gone. She is 10 years old, so lovely and loyal. She had accompanied my litter sister for her hard times, glew up with her, and gave us lots of laughts and joys.</p>\r\nWe buried her on the top of the moutain beside our house, face WuZhou''s famous Dragon Mother''s Temple.We hope her like the place.\r\n\r\nFarewell WangWang, may you rest in peace. You lives in our hearts forever.', 'To our dear WangWang', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'to-our-dear-wangwang', '', '', '2008-02-13 21:09:23', '2008-02-14 02:09:23', '', 0, 'http://sealence.x10hosting.com/wordpress/?p=41', 0, 'post', '', 0),
