(44, 1, '2008-02-15 08:53:06', '2008-02-15 13:53:06', '<p class="dropcap">\r\nWhen you come to China for the 2008 Olympic Games, there is one firefox plugin you must need. ''Cos lots of websites has been bend by the well known - G F W, use this Gladder plugin, firefox can change proxy for you automatically.</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p class="addon-feature-tagline"><a href="https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/2864" target="_blank">Gladder is a proxy tool works on a customizable sites list!</a></p>\r\nGet over G F W with Great Ladder!\r\n\r\nGladder is a proxy tool works on a customizable sites list.\r\n\r\nwith it, you can:\r\n* visit wikipedia.org and its sister sites\r\n* visit google cached page\r\n* visit gmail and orkut more stably (with https connection)\r\n* with one click, add a site to a list then any page in the site will be opened with a web proxy</blockquote>\r\nbut it can not see flash movies now... :cry:', 'Gladder, a firefox plugin you will need in China', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gladder-a-firefox-plugin-you-will-need-in-china', '', '', '2008-02-16 04:49:05', '2008-02-16 09:49:05', '', 0, 'http://sealence.x10hosting.com/wordpress/?p=44', 0, 'post', '', 2),
(52, 1, '2008-09-15 20:52:53', '2008-09-16 01:52:53', '\r\n<p class="dropcap">When using CGI::Application for web MVC Controller, It''s very important to prevent IE caches for Ajax request. Lucky we can do this on the <strong>cgiapp_prerun</strong> event, just a few lines of codes will do the trick:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre line="1" lang="perl">\r\nsub cgiapp_prerun {\r\n    my $self = shift;\r\n    $self->header_props(\r\n        # date in the past\r\n        -expires       => ''Sat, 26 Jul 1997 05:00:00 GMT'',\r\n        # HTTP/1.0\r\n        -Pragma        => ''no-cache'',\r\n        # HTTP/1.1\r\n        -Cache_Control => join('', '', qw(\r\n                no-store\r\n                no-cache\r\n                must-revalidate\r\n                post-check=0\r\n                pre-check=0\r\n        )),\r\n    );\r\n}</pre>', 'CGI::Application prevent IE caches for Ajax', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cgiapplication-prevent-ie-caches-for-ajax', '', '', '2008-09-16 01:05:09', '2008-09-16 06:05:09', '', 0, 'http://sealence.x10hosting.com/wordpress/?p=52', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(45, 1, '2008-02-21 08:26:45', '2008-02-21 13:26:45', '\r\n<p dragover="true" class="dropcap">Talking about rice noodles, you might thinking of the rice noodle of Guilin, but today what I''m gonna introduce to you is another rice noodle - Liuzhou Rice Noodles in Snail Soup.</p>\r\n<p dragover="true">Liuzhou Rice Noodles in Snail Soup is known to all, it has special tastes. Rice noodles in snail soup, having sour, peppery, refreshing, hot and fresh flavor, ranks the first in Liuzhou flavor snacks, it adopts special soft &amp; smooth refreshing rice noodles as materials and is prepared with sour bamboo shoots, agarics, peanuts, deep fry dried bean rolls, day lily, fresh tender vegetable etc. and rich proper pepper taste and snail boiled soup, one is drenched in sweat after eating, but you try to stop eating but cannot for its fresh snail soup leading a person to endless aftertastes.</p>\r\n<p dragover="true"><img src="http://sealence.x10hosting.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2008/02/r1.jpg" alt="noodle1" /></p>\r\n<p dragover="true">Man, I really can''t stop eating, this picture even make my mouth water! When you come to Guangxi province of China, cities such as Liuzhou/Guilin/Nanning, you gotta try this wonderful noodle. It''s my King of noodles! :D</p>', 'Liuzhou Rice Noodles in Snail Soup', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'spiral-rice-noodle', '', '', '2008-02-21 09:09:00', '2008-02-21 14:09:00', '', 0, 'http://sealence.x10hosting.com/wordpress/?p=45', 0, 'post', '', 2),
